.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, poker, domino, bridge, monopoly, chess, canasta
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the mexican is between the person playing domino and the pakistani##2
 7. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person playing poker is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Game      | domino    | monopoly  | bridge  | scrabble  | canasta      | chess       | poker |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

