.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, blue, turquise, yellow, aquamarine, red
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes white##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person who likes red and the person who likes blood-red##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes turquise##1
9. the person who likes yellow is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Color   | turquise      | yellow | blood-red | blue | red      | white      | aquamarine |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

