The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, soul, ambient, salsa, metal, house, jazz
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the fan of metal##1
