 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of ambient is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of indie##1
 8. the fan of house is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the fan of metal##2
10. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | soul    | salsa | ambient   | house | jazz    | metal |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

