.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
7 different games are played: canasta, poker, billiard, scrabble, monopoly, whist, go
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
11. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade   | cola         | fanta     | water              | mirinda    | juice     |
| Game        | whist | poker | monopoly | scrabble | go | canasta | billiard |

