3. the person watching romance movies is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
