6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
8. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is photography##2
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
